nodes.text: Nu was a letter in the Tionese alphabet. Nu was often used as a call sign for Imperial starfighter Flight groups, specifically Assault Gunboats. Assault Gunboat designated Nu 1 is one such example.

Nu was also a common surname—whether related to the letter or not—that was shared by many individuals within the galaxy, such as Jocasta Nu, Koobis Nu, and Risso Nu, as well as the given name of the Ithorian Nu Toreena.
